data.description: Discover the epitome of luxury and comfort in this stunning 4-bed, 3.5-bath Colonial home in Michigan. With a vaulted ceiling in the master suite and closet organizers in every room, elegance meets functionality. The spacious kitchen-dining-family area is perfect for gatherings, while separate living and dining rooms offer versatility. Step onto the expansive multi-level deck, newly resurfaced in '21/22, for unforgettable outdoor entertainment. The walkout basement boasts a full wet bar with a mahogany top, stainless steel cabinets, a wine fridge, and a hot tub on the stamped concrete patio below. With a high-efficiency furnace and hot water tank installed in '22, plus wired alarm security, this home is the complete package. Make this haven yours call today.
